cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is about object recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a new learning framework and optimization method, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The three tasks that the approach is applied to (eye localization, car detection, and object tracking) are all related to multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, and cs.RO.
